 Death landed at the base. It was not familiar but he knew destructor and it 
could only mean an advantage. All the horsmen created eachother. Once again 
reunited. Destructor also said hello. Suddenly the origanal 5 looked up in 
pure terror. They all looked at the tm2 dragon landing at thier feet. 
"Apocalypse!" those would be the last words of the once great 
destructor....Apocalypse grabbed him by the throat and proceeded to rip off 
his head. Apocalypse wiped the mech fluid of his hands. He turned to Kit Kat. 
"My name is apocalypse. We have much to discuss. Destructor was a weak being. 
Now the real war can begin." all the horsmen bowed on all fours to thier new 
master. War looked up with a tear in his eye and one thought in his 
head.."Destructor will be reseracted. When the day is right."
